; Square-shaped tumuli (双方中円墳) * {{ill|Kushiyama Kofun|ja|櫛山古墳|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kushiyama Kofun|qq=}} (150 meters) == See Also == * {{ill|Yamato Kofun Group|ja|大和古墳群|1=Ōyamato Kofun Group|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Kofun Group|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōyamato Kofun Group|qq=}}
